OL,3,C'Two can play at that game': Vance
OL,4,Caccuses Iran of 'economic terrorism'
OL,6,FUS Vice President JD Vance has said
OL,7,Fthe ball is in Tehran's court after
OL,8,Fthe start of a naval blockade of all
OL,9,FIranian ports.
OL,11,FThe blockade, which President Donald
OL,12,FTrump said came into effect on Monday,
OL,13,Fcame after negotiations in Pakistan
OL,14,Fover the weekend failed to reach a
OL,15,Fbreakthrough.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776255072
OL,3,C'Two can play at that game': Vance
OL,4,Caccuses Iran of 'economic terrorism'
OL,6,FIt also comes well over a month after
OL,7,FIran imposed an effective blockade of
OL,8,Fships passing through the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz ` a crucial shipping channel
OL,10,Fthrough which about a fifth of the
OL,11,Fworld's oil passes.
OL,13,FIran insists that it is only
OL,14,Fpreventing American ships and those of
OL,15,FUS allies, but maritime data shows
OL,16,Ftraffic has fallen sharply since the
OL,17,Fwar began, and the move has sent
OL,18,Fshockwaves through the global economy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776255072
OL,3,C'Two can play at that game': Vance
OL,4,Caccuses Iran of 'economic terrorism'
OL,6,FIn an interview with Fox News on
OL,7,FMonday night, Vance said: "What they
OL,8,Fhave done is engage in this act of
OL,9,Feconomic terrorism against the entire
OL,10,Fworld.
OL,12,F"They've basically threatened any ship
OL,13,Fthat's moving through the Straits of
OL,14,FHormuz. Well, as the President of the
OL,15,FUnited States showed, two can play at
OL,16,Fthat game."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776255072
OL,3,C'Two can play at that game': Vance
OL,4,Caccuses Iran of 'economic terrorism'
OL,6,FVance told Fox's "Special Report"
OL,7,Fprogramme that some progress with
OL,8,FIranian negotiators was made in
OL,9,FPakistan over the weekend, adding:
OL,10,F"The ball is very much in their court."
OL,12,FBritish Chancellor Rachel Reeves said
OL,13,Ffamilies and businesses across Britain
OL,14,Fare bearing the cost of instability
OL,15,F"they did not cause" as she headed to
OL,16,Fthe International Monetary Fund's
OL,17,Fspring meetings in Washington DC.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776255072
OL,3,C'Two can play at that game': Vance
OL,4,Caccuses Iran of 'economic terrorism'
OL,6,FThere, she is set to urge coordinated
OL,7,Faction to tackle the global economic
OL,8,Fshock caused by the Iran conflict,
OL,9,Fwhich has seen a spike in energy
OL,10,Fprices.
OL,12,FThe war could leave the average UK
OL,13,Fhousehold #480 worse off over the
OL,14,Fcurrent financial year, the Resolution
OL,15,FFoundation think tank has said.
OL,17,F"The Iran conflict must be a line in
OL,18,Fthe sand on how we deal with global
OL,19,Fcrisis and instability," she said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776255072
OL,3,C'Two can play at that game': Vance
OL,4,Caccuses Iran of 'economic terrorism'
OL,6,F"I will go to America with a clear
OL,7,Fmessage: global leaders must take co-
OL,8,Fordinated economic action and
OL,9,Fsupercharge the path to energy
OL,10,Fsecurity to protect ourselves in the
OL,11,Ffuture."
OL,13,FPakistan has proposed hosting a second
OL,14,Fround of talks between the United
OL,15,FStates and Iran in Islamabad in the
OL,16,Fcoming days, before the end of the
OL,17,Fceasefire, two Pakistani officials
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
