CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776255072
OL,3,C'Two can play at that game': Vance
OL,4,Caccuses Iran of 'economic terrorism'
OL,6,FThe officials, who spoke on condition
OL,7,Fof anonymity, said the proposal would
OL,8,Fdepend on whether the parties request
OL,9,Fa different location.
OL,11,FOne of the officials said that,
OL,12,Fdespite ending without an agreement,
OL,13,Fthe first talks were part of an
OL,14,Fongoing diplomatic process rather than
OL,15,Fa one-off effort.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
