PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776255072
OL,3,C'Two can play at that game': Vance
OL,4,Caccuses Iran of 'economic terrorism'
OL,6,FWhite House press secretary Karoline
OL,7,FLeavitt remained tight lipped when
OL,8,Fasked if new talks were being
OL,9,Fconsidered, telling reporters:
OL,10,F"President Trump, Vice President Vance
OL,11,Fand the negotiating team have made the
OL,12,FUS red lines very clear.
OL,14,F"The Iranians' desperation for a deal
OL,15,Fwill only increase with President
OL,16,FTrump's highly effective Naval
OL,17,Fblockade now in effect."
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
