PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776255072
OL,3,C'Two can play at that game': Vance
OL,4,Caccuses Iran of 'economic terrorism'
OL,6,FIn a warning to Iran, writing on his
OL,7,FTruth Social platform on Monday, Trump
OL,8,Fsaid: "If any of these ships come
OL,9,Fanywhere close to our BLOCKADE, they
OL,10,Fwill be immediately ELIMINATED, using
OL,11,Fthe same system of kill that we use
OL,12,Fagainst the drug dealers on boats at
OL,13,FSea."
OL,15,FDespite the threat, Trump told
OL,16,Freporters outside the Oval Office
OL,17,Flater on Monday that the US is still
OL,18,Fwilling to engage with Iran to
OL,19,Fnegotiate a resolution.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776255072
OL,3,C'Two can play at that game': Vance
OL,4,Caccuses Iran of 'economic terrorism'
OL,6,F"I can tell you that we've been called
OL,7,Fby the other side," Trump said,
OL,8,Fadding, "We've been called this
OL,9,Fmorning by the right people, the
OL,10,Fappropriate people, and they want to
OL,11,Fwork a deal."
OL,13,FIranian foreign ministry spokesperson
OL,14,FEsmaeil Baqaei derided the blockade as
OL,15,Fa "revenge of choice" against the
OL,16,Fglobal economy.
OL,18,F"Is it ever worthwhile to cut off
OL,19,Fone's nose to spite one's face?!" he
OL,20,Fwrote on X.
