OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FMeanwhile Iran's representative to the
OL,12,FUnited Nations has demanded
OL,13,Fcompensation from countries it says
OL,14,Fparticipated in the US and Israeli war
OL,15,Feffort against Iran.
OL,17,FIran's state media included Bahrain,
OL,18,FSaudi Arabia, Qatar, the United Arab
OL,19,FEmirates and Jordan in its list of
OL,20,Fcountries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
