PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776255072
OL,3,C'Two can play at that game': Vance
OL,4,Caccuses Iran of 'economic terrorism'
OL,6,FUN representative Amir-Saeid Iravani
OL,7,Fclaimed the countries had violated
OL,8,Finternational law and had to "make
OL,9,Ffull compensation for the damages
OL,10,Fcaused to the Islamic Republic of
OL,11,FIran, including payment of
OL,12,Fcompensation for all material and
OL,13,Fmoral damages resulting from their
OL,14,Finternational violation," Iran's
OL,15,Fofficial IRNA news agency reported.
OL,26,@pD@^OUvD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
