OL,3,C'Two can play at that game': Vance
OL,4,Caccuses Iran of 'economic terrorism'
OL,6,FWhile the delicate ceasefire with Iran
OL,7,Fis holding for now, Israel has
OL,8,Fcontinued its attacks on Iran-backed
OL,9,FHezbollah militant in Lebanon, which
OL,10,Fhas seen the displacement of around
OL,11,Fone million people.
OL,13,FSince the latest Middle East conflict
OL,14,Fbegan on February 28, an estimated
OL,15,F2,089 people have been killed by
OL,16,Fairstrikes in Lebanon, according to
OL,17,Fthe country's health ministry,
OL,18,Fincluding 252 women, 166 children, and
OL,19,F88 medical workers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
